description: Please note: This cell line was previously described as a neuroepithelioma (ATCC HTB-10). However recent evidence reveals it is Ewing's Sarcoma (http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15548687, http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/biosample/3151999,http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25453903)
summary: Homo sapiens SK-N-MC immortalized cell line
